{"tid":1447924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:24.000Z","uid":86115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0519de922e9bc4c7dcdb49dcc6572aa2fcf8daec","tid":1447924,"uid":86115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=eaea8ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=31d161a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"5dc0acd3adba76168e750ee947ece84c49413a20","tid":1447924,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"982e39acfe0d6898abd6c9ecde9b990c57e59750","tid":1447924,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"121666c3a226b3b4e128fad94c9603e31eed8037","tid":1447924,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a81aa525d6eb8d866e86c08867640416230b156","tid":1447924,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019